                <pb facs="1439" n="1415" xml:id="pg_1415"/>
                <p rend="flushleft">I. <hi rend="italic">Records of Previous Meetings</hi>
                </p>
                <p>It was <hi rend="italic">decided</hi> to approve the records of the decisions
                    taken by the Council of Foreign Ministers at the 1st, 2nd, 3rd, 4th, 5th, 6th,
                    7th, 8th and 9th Meetings of the Third Session, held in New York.</p>
                <p rend="flushleft">II. <hi rend="italic">Report of the Deputies</hi>
                </p>
                <p>The report submitted by the Acting Chairman of the Deputies was considered. (See
                        <gloss target="#t_CFMD46NY1">CFM(D) (46) (NY)</gloss> 127Meeting, December
                    4, 1946.)<note n="61" xml:id="d382fn61">Not printed; the substance of the
                        Deputies’ Report is recorded in the United States Delegation Minutes, <hi rend="italic">supra.</hi>
                    </note>
                </p>
                <p rend="flushleft">III. <hi rend="italic">Article 76 of the Draft Treaty With
                        Italy</hi>
                </p>
                <p>It was <hi rend="italic">decided</hi> to adopt the text of Article 76 (Annex
                        l).<note n="62" xml:id="d382fn62">Annex 1 of this Record is not printed.
                        Article 76 of the Italian Treaty, as presented to and adopted by the Council
                        at this meeting, was included in the Treaty of Peace with Italy as article
                        87.</note>
                </p>
                <p rend="flushleft">IV. <hi rend="italic">Draft Peace Treaty With Italy, Article 16
                        bis. Draft Instrument for the Provisional Regime</hi> (<gloss target="#t_CFM46NY1">CFM(46) (NY)</gloss>43)<note n="63" xml:id="d382fn63">Under consideration at this point is <gloss target="#t_CFM46NY1">CFM (46)
                            (NY)</gloss>43 (Revised), December 4, 1946, <hi rend="italic">infra.</hi>
                    </note>
                </p>
                <p>1. <hi rend="italic">Article 14</hi> (now Article 10 in <gloss target="#t_CFM46NY1">CFM(46) (NY)</gloss>43 revised December 4)</p>
                <p>It was <hi rend="italic">decided</hi> to adopt the text of Paragraph 10 of the
                    Draft Instrument for the Provisional Regime annex to Article 16 bis (Annex
                    2).</p>
                <p>2. <hi rend="italic">Article 13</hi> (now Article 9 in <gloss target="#t_CFM46NY1">CFM(46) (NY)</gloss>43 revised December 4)</p>
                <p>After an exchange of views, it was <hi rend="italic">decided</hi> to refer
                    Paragraph 13 for joint study by the Sub-Committee on Trieste and the Economic
                    Experts.</p>
                <p>3. <hi rend="italic">Article 6</hi> (no change in number)</p>
                <p>It was <hi rend="italic">decided</hi> to approve the text submitted by the
                    Military Experts. (See <gloss target="#t_CFM46NY1">CFM(46) (NY)</gloss>48)<note n="64" xml:id="d382fn64">The text of the redrafted article 6 is included in
                        footnote 67, <ref target="#pg_1418">p. 1418</ref>.</note>
                </p>
                <p rend="flushleft">V. <hi rend="italic">Reparation by Italy for Yugoslavia, Greece,
                        Albania and Ethiopia and Reparation by Bulgaria for Yugoslavia and
                        Greece</hi>
                </p>
                <p>After an exchange of views, a decision on this question was <hi rend="italic">deferred.</hi>
                </p>
                <p rend="flushleft">VI. <hi rend="italic">Compensation for Damage to United Nations’
                        Property on the Territory of Italy, Roumania, Hungary, Bulgaria and
                        Finland</hi>
                </p>
                <p>After an exchange of views, a decision on this question was <hi rend="italic">deferred.</hi>
                </p>
                <p rend="flushleft">VII. <hi rend="italic">Fair Prices-Reparation Deliveries From
                        Roumania</hi>
                </p>
                <p>After an exchange of views a decision on this question was <hi rend="italic">deferred.</hi>
                </p>
